The '''Illuminated One''' was the leader of the [[Charon/Legends|Charon]] [[Cult of Light]] sometime before the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. The Illuminated One preached that he and his kindred needed to escape the known galaxy to escape the grasp of their doom-bringing brethren in the [[Charon Death Cult]]. The Illuminated One formulated a plan to ensure the survival of his kind after the Cult of Light discovered [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] technology.

